PAPERWALLS — CURSOR RULES
==========================

Project structure: Next.js 14, App Router, TypeScript, located in /src

NEVER TOUCH THESE — ever, for any reason:
  src/app/api/          ← PayFast, checkout, Supabase routes
  src/lib/              ← business logic, pricing, storage
  src/middleware.ts     ← auth
  src/types/            ← TypeScript types
  src/contexts/         ← CartContext
  src/app/page.tsx      ← landing page (uses its own CSS class system)

BRAND NAME: always "Paperwalls" — capital P, capital W, one word. Never "paperwalls" or "PaperWalls"

COLOUR TOKENS — always use pw-* Tailwind tokens. Never stone-*, never hardcode hex:
  bg-pw-bg / text-pw-bg           #F8F4EF  page background
  bg-pw-surface                   #FFFFFF  cards, panels
  bg-pw-ink / text-pw-ink         #1A1714  primary text, dark fills
  text-pw-muted                   #8A8175  secondary text, labels
  bg-pw-accent / text-pw-accent   #C4622D  terracotta brand colour
  bg-pw-accent-soft               #F2E8E1  blush backgrounds
  bg-pw-stone                     #E6DFD8  warm grey

TYPOGRAPHY:
  H1: text-3xl font-bold text-pw-ink
  H2: text-2xl font-bold text-pw-ink
  Body: text-pw-ink font-light leading-relaxed
  Labels/eyebrow: text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-pw-muted

BUTTONS:
  Primary:  bg-pw-ink text-white rounded-pw hover:bg-pw-ink-soft
  Accent:   bg-pw-accent text-white rounded-pw hover:opacity-90
  Outline:  border border-pw-ink text-pw-ink bg-transparent rounded-pw
  NEVER rounded-full on buttons. Always rounded-pw.

CARDS: rounded-pw-card (never rounded-2xl or rounded-xl)
FOCUS RINGS: focus:border-pw-ink focus:ring-1 focus:ring-pw-ink (never amber, never pink)

ADMIN PAGES: follow the same token rules. Admin is not exempt.